 and uplifting . the film itself is almost a reversal of the life of george bailey -- there isn ' t too much to it , but capra and the gang ( various screenwriters , composers , actors ) plumet the material to its fullest potential . the result is a film -- though not at first intended to be pigeon - holed as a holiday film -- that will always be remembered , celebrated , and loved .|uplifting
